      "duration": "1 minute/level",
      "damageFormula": "",
      "healFormula": "",
      "savingThrow": "none",
      "effect": "This spell creates an animated +2 flaming burst greatsword. The sword appears where the caster designates and attacks any opponent within range once per round, beginning on the round in which it appears. Its attack bonus is equal to the caster’s base attack bonus + the caster’s Int bonus. The sword can be directed not to attack or to attack only particular enemies, to return to the caster’s side, or to guard the caster. Each round, the caster can use a free action to redirect the sword. If not commanded, it continues to follow its last command. Once a target is destroyed, or if the sword leaves the spell range or is not directed, it returns to the caster and hovers near her as if it were commanded to guard. The flaming sword of Xuzl can be used to create a flanking situation against an opponent if it attacks opposite an ally.",
