        "feats": "Bejeweled elementals receive Cleave, Dual Wield, Improved Two-Weapon Fighting, and Sunder as bonus feats. Even when attacking with Dual Wield, bejeweled elementals get 1.5 times their Strength bonus to damage on their primary slam",
        "climateTerrain": "Any",
