        "attacks": "Slam +21/+16/+11 melee, off-hand slam +16 melee",
        "damage": "Slam 2d10+13 and 1d8 fire plus lava splash proc, of fhand slam 2d10+4 and 1d8 fire plus lava splash proc 5 ft. by 5 Ft./10 Ft. Lava splash Elemental, lava aura (6), fire subtype Fort +16, Ref +12, Will +6 Str 27, Dex 12, Con 21, Int 6, Wis 11, Cha 11 Intimidate +10, Listen +12, Spot +12, Taunt +10 Dual Wield, Power Attack, Riposte, Sunder Any Solitary 7 None",
