        "feats": "As shown in their statistics below, \"pure\" elementals (those of air, earth, fire, or water) gain a number of bonus feats as they become more powerful. Fast Recovery (Ex): Elementals recover a number of hit points equal to their HD for each hour of rest or light activity. Engaging in",
